### =========================================================
### NOTES
### - All create/update endpoints below are multipart/form-data because controller uses [FromForm]
### - For array fields like TagIds, repeat the same form key multiple times
### - For requests with statementFile, comment out descriptionMd fields
### - For requests with descriptionMd, do not send statementFile
### =========================================================

### 1) CREATE PROBLEM (normal) - markdown mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/Problems
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=CreateProblemBoundary

--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Title"

Two Sum Basic
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Slug"

two-sum-basic
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Difficulty"

easy
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="TypeCode"

algorithm
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ScoringCode"

acm
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="TimeLimitMs"

1000
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="MemoryLimitKb"

262144
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="DescriptionMd"

Given an array of integers, return indices of two numbers such that they add up to target.
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ProblemMode"

pro
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="TagIds"

{{tagId1}}
--CreateProblemBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="TagIds"

{{tagId2}}
--CreateProblemBoundary--

